<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>날씨</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #D8CEF6;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 20px;
            color: black;
            margin-left: 250px;
        }
        .sidebar {
            width: 250px;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            position: fixed;
            height: 100%;
            border: 1px solid #d3d3d3;
        }
        .sidebar a {
            padding-top: 15px;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 18px;           
	        text-align: center;
            color: black;
            display: block;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #d3d3d3;
        }
        .sidebar a:hover {
            background-color: #d3d3d3;
            color: black;
        }
        .main-content h2 {
            margin-left: 30px;
        }
        .main-content h3 {
            margin-left: 30px;
        }
        .main-content {
            margin-left: 270px;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .weather-card {
            margin-left: 30px;
	    margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 300px;
            text-align: center;           
	    margin-top: 20px;
            background: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .weather-card p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .weather-card .location {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .weather-card .temp {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-top: 10px;
	        margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
	    .weekly-weather {
            margin-top: 70px;
        }
	    .cta-message {
            margin-top: -120px;
	        text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        관리자 페이지
    </div>
    <div class="sidebar">
        <a href="#">HOME</a>
        <a href="#">통계</a>
        <a href="#">공지사항</a>
        <a href="#">날씨</a>
        <a href="#">...</a>   
    </div>
    <div class="main-content">
        <h2>현재 날씨</h2>
        <% if (weatherData) { %>
            <div class="weather-card">
                <div class="location"><%= weatherData.name %> / <%= weatherData.sys.country %></div>
                <div class="temp"><%= weatherData.main.temp %> ℃</div>
                <p><%= weatherData.weather[0].description %></p>
            </div>
        <% } else if (error) { %>
            <p><%= error %></p>
        <% } else { %>
            <p>날씨 정보를 가져오는 중...</p>
        <% } %>

        <div class="weekly-weather">
            <h2>일주일 날씨</h2>
	    <div id="id952023c65f289" a='{"t":"r","v":"1.2","lang":"ko","locs":[873],"ssot":"c","sics":"ds","cbkg":"#FFFFFF","cfnt":"#000000","codd":"#FFFFFF","cont":"#000000d4","etp":"bool"}' style="width: 1100px; height: 305px;">날씨 데이터 소스: <a href="https://sharpweather.com/weather_seoul/30_days/">weather 30 days Seoul</a></div>
	    <script async src="https://static1.sharpweather.com/widgetjs/?id=id952023c65f289"></script>
	</div>
    	
	<div class="cta-message">
            <h3>날씨를 확인하고 세탁하세요!</h3>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
